r high-spin halos could point to a role of large-scale tidal\nfields in the evolution of the spin PDF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Mar 2010 20:06:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Jul 2010 14:51:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2010 09:58:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
