rcuitry. It also enables the realization of multi-valued logic, significantly\nincreasing the complexity of computer circuits by allowing several neuro-bits\nto be transmitted on a single wire.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 20 Mar 2010 15:02:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-10-27"}
